entry.title: Ukraine Runs Into Russian Air Superiority
entry.content: Kyiv said its forces were advancing on several axes in their counteroffensive but were struggling to counter Russian airpower and artillery hobbling its assaults in the east and south.

entry.title: Tattered and Bandaged, Russian POWs Describe Ukraine's Offensive
entry.content: The first battles in Ukraine’s big offensive, aimed at retaking land in the country’s south and east occupied by Russia, are yielding a steady flow of Russian prisoners.
